---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Us"
    description="Learn more about the team behind NZ Security Directory and how we can help you find the best security installation companies in New Zealand.">
    
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About NZ Security Directory</h1>
        
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">NZ Security Directory is New Zealand's premier platform connecting homeowners and businesses with trusted security installation professionals. We understand that finding the right security provider can be challenging, which is why we've created a comprehensive directory of verified security companies across New Zealand.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Our mission is to simplify the process of finding and comparing security installation services in New Zealand. We believe everyone deserves access to reliable security solutions, and we're committed to making that process as transparent and straightforward as possible.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Verified Providers</h3>
                    <p>We carefully vet all security companies listed in our directory to ensure they meet our quality standards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Local Expertise</h3>
                    <p>Find security providers in your area who understand your specific needs and local requirements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Comprehensive Information</h3>
                    <p>Access detailed company profiles, services offered, and customer reviews all in one place.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Free Resource</h3>
                    <p>Our directory is completely free to use, helping you make informed decisions about your security needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you. Contact our team at [contact information] or use our contact form below.</p>
            <!-- Add contact form component here if desired -->
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                    Contact Us
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>